description:
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a Band 4 Nursing Associate to join our friendly team within the Dermatology Outpatients Department based at Arndale House. We are seeking a motivated and enthusiastic individual who can demonstrate the values of the Trust; Care, Respect and Responsibility.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will be involved in all aspects of the Dermatology Outpatient Service, including Phototherapy, Skin surgery, Patch test, Wound care and Outpatient clinics, supporting patients and staff to ensure the highest standard of patient care is delivered. You should possess excellent communication skills and demonstrate a caring attitude. Full training and support will be provided for all aspects of the roll, offering you an opportunity to develop a wide range of knowledge and skills.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Philippa Tinsley - Clinical Operations Lead&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;philippa.tinsley@ldh.nhs.uk Telephone number 01582 497229&lt;/p&gt;
